Subject: Upgrade fail
Description: When we tried to apply this update : "EPP Server Hotfix #1 - Important Security Updates for EPP Server (HWA-EPP4-U8800)" the installation seems to be ok, when finished the update page said that there no more update but going to another page and came back to the update page, the update is still present
Solution_Comment__c: update didn't disappear after it was applied, explained that it will disappear after 5.9.4 update
